title: Peaceful Back Corner One Bedroom at the Historic Grand Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '1962 Grand Ave - 104 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available 10/1: Peaceful & spacious one-bedroom apartment home in the heart of Grand Ave!', 'This back corner one-bedroom apartment home sits on an elevated first floor, & features large windows that bring in a lot of natural sunlight.', 'Your new home features hardwood floors throughout the apartment, ample closet space, & original built-in cabinets that give the apartment the vintage charm Grand Ave is known for.', 'Experience the Grand Avenue life at The Historic Grand Apartments.', 'Located in between Macalester College and the University of St. Thomas, the Historic Grand Apartments offer one-bedroom apartments that are within walking distance from the many fine restaurants and shops located along Grand Avenue.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Heat/Water/Trash Paid', '24/7 Emergency Maintenance', 'Controlled Entry', 'On-Site Laundry', 'Smoke-Free Building', 'Cats Welcome', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 700', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,014.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
